maintext:
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday afternoon’s drawing of the Connecticut Lottery’s “Lucky Links Day” game were:
01-05-07-11-15-18-19-22
(one, five, seven, eleven, fifteen, eighteen, nineteen, twenty-two)
